\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 4. **Full GitOps integration** with GitHub Actions and clinical review workflows
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 5. **Production-grade monitoring** with Prometheus metrics and Grafana dashboards
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 6. **Error recovery mechanisms** with automated rollback capabilities
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 7. **Performance optimizations** through parallel processing
\f1\fs24 \
\

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 The solution is specifically tailored for Australian healthcare with support for SNOMED CT-AU, AMT, and ICD-10-AM, while maintaining compatibility with international standards like LOINC and RxNorm.
